column3: L1, L2 = maximum dimension of zircon (including tips) (in two orientations; mean used)
W1, W2 = mutually perpendicular widths of orthorhombic prism or equatorial diameters
h1, h2 = "tip" heights of pyramidal terminations
apatite: 2 = both tips present, 1 = one tip missing, 0 = both tips missing, DUR = durango
